# Copy this file to scripts/.mirror-codenames (which is gitignored) and fill it
# in with the real private codenames. Consumed by scripts/check-mirror-codenames.sh.
#
# Format: one entry per line, PRIVATE_CODENAME|public-alias
#   - the alias is optional (leave it empty to detect-only)
#   - blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored
#   - PRIVATE_CODENAME is matched whole-word, case-sensitive
#
# The real file is gitignored on purpose so no private codename ever lands in
# either repo. This example carries only placeholders.
EXAMPLE_CLIENT_CODENAME|public-alias-to-use-instead
ANOTHER_CODENAME_NO_ALIAS|
